  <summary date="2021-09-12T15:02:42Z" status="Introduced in House">Stopping Appealing Flavors in E-Cigarettes for Kids Act or the SAFE Kids Act

This bill generally prohibits the inclusion of flavored products in non-cigarette tobacco products, including electronic nicotine delivery system (e.g., e-cigarettes and vape pens).</summary>
